{"tid":272464,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"JW﹕男友喜歡我嬌小玲瓏","createTime":"2017-06-06T00:05:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-07T00:00:03.000Z","uid":81228,"like":5,"dislike":92,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3a0a307d154586396954944803fd638be1b5faa2","tid":272464,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T00:05:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.mingpaocanada.com/tor/ftp/News/20170605/HK/_05MA013_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaocanada.com%2Ftor%2Fftp%2FNews%2F20170605%2FHK%2F_05MA013_.jpg&h=506cb3c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mingpaocanada.com/tor/ftp/News/20170605/HK/_05MA012_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaocanada.com%2Ftor%2Fftp%2FNews%2F20170605%2FHK%2F_05MA012_.jpg&h=4717a78a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【明報專訊】王灝兒(JW)和張繼聰昨晚為「生力啤酒節2017」演出，JW中午跟男友葉韋彤(Tarzan)在馬場齊齊拉頭馬賀朋友，再次被網友討論兩人的「最萌身高差」，JW說﹕「今日是朋友的馬匹跑贏，我同男友去替他開心，我第二次拉頭馬，也是第一次公開跟男友合照，其實他就是喜歡我的嬌小玲瓏，我的高度同身形他都鍾意，這些自信是他給我的。」問到JW是否同樣滿意男友身形？會否叫他減肥？她冧爆說﹕「我覺得他是完美，已經好好，我就是喜歡這樣的他。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>張繼聰fit爆騷肌</strong><br />\n<br />\n張繼聰身形明顯變得健碩，近年專注拍劇的他鮮有亮相音樂會，他說﹕「我的音樂事業很快就玩完啦，不過玩完都可以重來。」他直言跟主辦單位由2004年合作過，難得有機會演出，都可以滿足自己。問到太太謝安琪坐月後的情况？他說：「休息可以是無止境，坐月可以坐3個月，主力照顧小朋友，她是個盡責的媽媽，近來也有做運動，慢慢回復身材。」<br />\n<br />\n記者﹕楊安莉<br />\n攝影﹕林祖傑<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mingpaocanada.com/tor/htm/News/20170605/HK-mae1_r.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaocanada.com%2Ftor%2Fhtm%2FNews%2F20170605%2FHK-mae1_r.htm&d=Rq9gFWrYpwVjoItm5vmgSTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=d0e9acdd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mingpaocanada.com/tor/htm/News/20170605/HK-mae1_r.htm</a>"},{"pid":"cf7457c0dbe61a61d6897a84221d279be9f97b8a","tid":272464,"uid":62,"like":3,"dislike":28,"score":-25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T01:23:05.000Z","msg":"jw都好完美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細細粒 又靚 又cute<br />\n又有身材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\